verbose_text: Three days after stimulation, no difference in the expression of IL-4 or the transcription factor GATA-3 was observed between WT and IL-31RA KO mice under Th2 polarizing condition (XREF_FIG B), indicating that IL-31RA signaling does not regulate Th2 differentiation.
evidence: expression of IL-4 or the transcription factor GATA-3
